{"tid":1426831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【上過前線請入】只要係人 就會攰","createTime":"2019-08-07T04:00:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T11:51:41.000Z","uid":187717,"like":52,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"139a5e28956f9962f7ff770127759ab5cc4bc6a4","tid":1426831,"uid":187717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:00:59.000Z","msg":"利申左先：我起8.5有份做滅火隊<br />\n<br />\n我見到咩？大家好團結 但唔止呢樣<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我見到前線好撚攰</span></span><br />\n長久不停既戰鬥+冇合適既方法做情緒緩衝，令所有手足都開始麻木<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">原本我都係呢班麻木左既人之一</span>發現自己開始分唔清對錯，唔知自己做既野有咩成效、有咩好/壞影響。仲要尋日有個女義士比呀叔鬧就想上前同呀叔隻揪⋯⋯好彩我地拉番佢番來<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咁搞法我地同班狗有咩分別？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我原本都迷惘，但我去睇一睇6,7,8月同反送中有關既鏗鏘集之後，我發現我地開始<span style=\"color: red;\">每場集會都變勇武</span>，甚至勇武次數多到<span style=\"color: red;\">不能理解</span>（睇完鏗鏘集再睇返自己之前見到既活動，已經冇左明顯大型純粹和理非）<br />\n<br />\n之前講好既和理非+勇武才是致勝關鍵呢？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而家啲人睇唔到成日覺得亂呀屌</span><br />\n<br />\n所以⋯⋯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mDD9PJC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmDD9PJC.png&h=5bc88b40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而家係和理非回合<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各位義士差下電 之後再戰！</span></span>"},{"pid":"d0afeb8f068ff25f597cdbafc4e6107545e0036e","tid":1426831,"uid":183649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:03:26.000Z","msg":"好攰<br />\n但我愛我既下一代<br />\n加油"},{"pid":"402114cd7796fff0a953a7781e058442759a0d3a","tid":1426831,"uid":238275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:04:52.000Z","msg":"推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推推"},{"pid":"1badc89b78337c8f3a8e56094c77676ce470bd02","tid":1426831,"uid":293698,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"re